article.headline: Sherfield scores 23 to lead Nevada over Fresno St. 73-57
article.linkText: Sherfield scores 23 to lead Nevada over Fresno St. 73-57
article.story: RENO, Nev. -- — Grant Sherfield had 23 points as Nevada beat Fresno State 73-57 on Friday night. Desmond Cambridge Jr. had 13 points for Nevada (9-5, 4-3 Mountain West Conference). Warren Washington added 13 points. Orlando Robinson had 15 points for the Bulldogs (5-4, 3-4). Isaiah Hill added 15 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
